hNumber":5542,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":null,"lang":"tr"},{"name":"74:48","price":"Artık şefaat edenlerin şefaatleri onlara yarar sağlamaz.","arabic":"فَمَا تَنفَعُهُمۡ شَفَٰعَةُ ٱلشَّٰفِعِينَ","category":["74 (Al-Muddathir)","Al-Muddathir","Surah Al-Muddathir"],"ayahNumber":5543,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":null,"lang":"tr"},{"name":"74:49","price":"Öyleyse onlara ne oluyor da öğütten yüz çeviriyorlar?","arabic":"فَمَا لَهُمۡ عَنِ ٱلتَّذۡكِرَةِ مُعۡرِضِينَ","category":["74 (Al-Muddathir)","Al-Muddathir","Surah Al-Muddathir"],"ayahNumber":5544,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":null,"lang":"tr"},{"name":"74:50","price":"Onlar adeta ürkütülmüş yaban eşekleri gibidir.","arabic":"كَأَنَّهُمۡ حُمُرٞ مُّسۡتَنفِرَةٞ","category":["74 (Al-Muddathir)","Al-Muddathir","Surah Al-Muddathir"],"ayahNumber":5545,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":null,"lang":"tr"},{"name":"74:51","price":"Aslandan ürküp, kaçan.","arabic":"فَرَّتۡ مِن قَسۡوَرَةِۭ","category":["74 (Al-Muddathir)","Al-Muddathir","Surah Al-Muddathir"],"ayahNumber":5546,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":null,"lang":"tr"},{"name":"74:52","price":"Hayır; her biri önüne açılıvermiş sahifeler verilmesini ister.","arabic":"بَلۡ يُرِيدُ كُلُّ ٱمۡرِيٕٖ مِّنۡهُمۡ أَن يُؤۡتَىٰ صُحُفٗا مُّنَشَّرَةٗ","category":["74 (Al-Muddathir)","Al-Muddathir","Surah Al-Muddathir"],"ayahNumber":5547,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":null,"lang":"tr"},{"name":"74:53","price":"Asla! Doğrusu onlar ahiretten korkmuyorlar.","arabic":"كَلَّاۖ بَل لَّا يَخَافُونَ ٱلۡأٓخِرَةَ","category":["74 (Al-Muddathir)","Al-Muddathir","Surah Al-Muddathir"],"ayahNumber":5548,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":null,"lang":"tr"},{"name":"74:54","price":"Hayır! Şüphesiz o (Kur'an) ancak bir öğüttür.","arabic":"كَلَّآ إِنَّهُۥ تَذۡكِرَةٞ","category":["74 (Al-Muddathir)","Al-Muddathir","Surah Al-Muddathir"],"ayahNumber":5549,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":null,"lang":"tr"},{"name":"74:55","price":"Artık dileyen kimse ondan öğüt alır.","arabic":"فَمَن شَآءَ ذَكَرَهُۥ","category":["74 (Al-Muddathir)","Al-Muddathir","Surah Al-Muddathir"],"ayahNumber":5550,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":null,"lang":"tr"},{"name":"74:56","price":"Allah dilemedikçe onlar öğüt almazlar. Kendisinden korkulmaya layık olan da, bağışlayıcı olan da O’dur.","arabic":"وَمَا يَذۡكُرُونَ إِلَّآ أَن يَشَآءَ ٱللَّهُۚ هُوَ أَهۡلُ ٱلتَّقۡوَىٰ وَأَهۡلُ ٱلۡمَغۡفِرَةِ","category":["74 (Al-Muddathir)","Al-Muddathir","Surah Al-Muddathir"],"ayahNumber":5551,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":null,"lang":"tr"}],"chapter":["74 (Al-Muddathir)","Al-Muddathir","Surah Al-Muddathir","Chapter Al-Muddathir","Muddathir","Surah Muddathir","Chapter Muddathir","Al Muddathir","Surah Al Muddathir","Chapter Al Muddathir","Surah 74","Chapter 74","The Cloaked One","المدثر"]}